criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Both sexes;

          -  Ages ranging from 7 to 11 years old;

          -  Mixed dentition;

          -  Maxillary constriction;

          -  No previous orthodontic treatment.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cleft lip and palate and associated syndromes;

          -  Systemic and/or neurological diseases.
